\"A report on the building was completed and presented to the local board in early September.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A report\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 572}, {\"ngram\": \"the building\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"the local board\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"early September\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The report concluded the building wasearthquake-proneand in need of significant structural improvements - for which it may have to close the facility to undertake.\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The report\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"the building wasearthquake-proneand\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"need\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"significant structural improvements\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"the facility\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It offered four options to the board.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four options\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of them was a recommendation to extend the lease until November 2026 alongside conducting detailed designs,with a temporary closure the following year for construction.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a recommendation\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"the lease\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"detailed designs\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"a temporary closure\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"construction\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An earlier condition assessment estimated the improvements would cost $5.3 million, but the report admitted the cost of capital works could decrease by 20% or balloon by 70% after designs are completed.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An earlier condition assessment\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"the improvements\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"the report\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"capital works\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"20%\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"balloon\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"70%\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"designs\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week, the board delayed the decision over the future of the facility until today where the item will be voted on in confidentiality at a meeting before being released to the public.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"the facility\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"the item\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"confidentiality\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"a meeting\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, not everyone is happy with the contents of the report.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"not everyone\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the contents\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"the report\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pool's director, Peter Rust, backed by over 30 supporters, rejected many of the claims in the report at the board's last meeting.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"score\": 0.9778382065549684, \"rank\": 0.022080675378052125, \"text\": \"Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rust\", \"score\": 0.9999999648425735, \"rank\": 3.515763018840205e-08, \"text\": \"Rust\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rust\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rust\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pool's director\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"over 30 supporters\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"the claims\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"the report\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"the board's last meeting\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He claimed the pool could be left open - and the company could pay for the construction in exchange for a 30-year lease extension.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"exchange\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"a 30-year lease extension\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have presented an outline of how to screen off the necessary work area for the seismic upgrading.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an outline\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"the necessary work area\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"the seismic upgrading\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can undertake that and complete it within two years.\\\"\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ross Walker, a self-proclaimed \\\"ordinary guy\\\" and regular user of the pool, said the Olympic Pool and Fitness Centre represented more than just a place to \\\"get fit\\\".\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1918, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1183286661375916e-15, \"text\": \"Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ross_Geller\"}, {\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\", \"score\": 0.9999900932952687, \"rank\": 9.906777449706826e-06, \"text\": \"Walker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kemba_Walker\"}, {\"begin\": 2003, \"end\": 2015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiapark_(Munich)\", \"score\": 0.675894116870583, \"rank\": 0.47950819672118666, \"text\": \"Olympic Pool\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiapark_(Munich)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiapark_(Munich)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a self-proclaimed \\\"ordinary guy\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"regular user\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"just a place\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He called it a \\\"community of communities\\\", made up of seniors attending yoga classes, young kids at swim classes, and the \\\"old Chinese spa social club\\\" who packed the spa every morning.\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2212, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8026137204333456, \"rank\": 0.2456847741745985, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\\"community\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"seniors\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"yoga classes\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"young kids\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"swim classes\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"the spa\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Closing this facility will destroy those communities.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this facility\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"those communities\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This facility provides important physical and mental wellbeing services for a variety of communities of Auckland.\\\"\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999008651, \"rank\": 7.762631660261475e-11, \"text\": \"Auckland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This facility\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"important physical and mental wellbeing services\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2398}, {\"ngram\": \"a variety\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Walker said a closure, even temporarily - would spell a permanent end for the pools.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Walker\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"a closure\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"a permanent end\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"the pools\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With five other gyms in the area, you are going to struggle to get that up and running again,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five other gyms\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are so many choices - and people do not change gyms readily.\\\"\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many choices\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"gyms\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The public was barred from being in the boardroom while further details of the report were discussed because of confidential material.\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The public\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"the boardroom\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2753}, {\"ngram\": \"further details\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2775}, {\"ngram\": \"the report\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"confidential material\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is understood critical information, which could ultimately influence members' decisions, is included in this material.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"critical information\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"members' decisions\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"this material\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Member Sarah Trotman appeared to include some of this in her line of questions.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2970, \"end\": 2983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Trotman\", \"score\": 0.9999855750201225, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Trotman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Trotman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Trotman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her line\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The lease agreement in 2005 required the leasee to spend $1.5 million on reviewing plant and equipment,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The lease agreement\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"the leasee\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3092}, {\"ngram\": \"plant\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The staff are implying that did not happen.\\\"\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The staff\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Board chair Genevieve Sage jumped in before Trotman could continue.\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3219, \"end\": 3228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Genevieve\", \"score\": 0.9999999998681233, \"rank\": 1.3170789186489383e-10, \"text\": \"Genevieve\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Genevieve\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Genevieve\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Trotman\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's the confidential report that you are talking about,\\\" Sage said.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the confidential report\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"Sage\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So perhaps that's something that we could discuss in confidentiality as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"confidentiality\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The public may not know the final outcome of the meeting until 5pm Tuesday.\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The public\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3445}, {\"ngram\": \"the final outcome\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3476}, {\"ngram\": \"the meeting\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jordan Dunn is a multimedia reporter based in Auckland with a focus on crime, social issues, policing and local issues.\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3512, \"end\": 3518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999183235519412, \"rank\": 4.7059737076146684e-05, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan\"}, {\"begin\": 3558, \"end\": 3566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999008651, \"rank\": 7.762631660261475e-11, \"text\": \"Auckland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a multimedia reporter\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3548}, {\"ngram\": \"a focus\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3579}, {\"ngram\": \"crime\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3588}, {\"ngram\": \"social issues\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"policing and local issues\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He joined Newstalk ZB in 2024 from Radio New Zealand, where he started as an intern out of the New Zealand Broadcasting School.\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3642, \"end\": 3653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newstalk_ZB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Newstalk ZB\", \"types\": [\"Q43229